Arija Bareikis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arija_Bareikis 0 Arija Allison Bareikis (born July 21, 1966) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Officer Chickie Brown in the TV crime drama Southland. She is also known for the films Deuce Bigalow: Male Gigolo and The Purge.
